Junk food news and some reviews!
Sister accounts: @food_oddity and @nostalgiahunting

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by CandyHunting on August 16, 2021. May be an image of food.

node.text: Keep an eye out for new Nashville Hot Cheetos! Thanks to my follower, Scott, for the image!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 16, 2021 tagging @oreo, @walmart, @mondelez_international, and @nabiscosnacks. May be an image of food.

node.text:
The new Apple Cider Donut Oreos officially launch today! I found them at Walmart.

The Oreos are more apple-forward than an apple cider donut, and that's fine by me! The flavor is a mix of apple and cinnamon. They're pretty darn tasty and worth picking up a pack.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 16, 2021 tagging @cinnabon. May be an image of ‎dessert, indoor and ‎text that says '‎سد CHOCOLATE CHIP COOKIE OUTSIDE CINNAMON ROLL INSIDE‎'‎‎.

node.text:
Cinnabon is bringing back their Cookie BonBites starting today for a limited time! The Cookie BonBites have a bite-sized cinnamon roll stuffed inside a chocolate chip cookie. These are available at Cinnabon locations inside malls and at Pilot Flying J Travel Centers. Additionally, the Cookie BonBites are now available for delivery on all food delivery platforms.

Thanks to Cinnabon's PR team for the news and images!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 15, 2021 tagging @redvinescandy, and @crackerbarrel. May be an image of food.

node.text: New Candy Corn flavored Red Vines are out now for Halloween! These are surprisingly delicious. They have a sweet honey-type flavor. I found them at Cracker Barrel.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 15, 2021 tagging @drpepper. May be an image of food and drink.

node.text:
Dr Pepper is launching a new, limited edition flavor exclusively through their new Pepper Perks rewards program! The new Dr Pepper FANtastic Chocolate flavor can be purchased by redeeming points collected through proof of purchase QR codes on Dr Pepper products. Visit drpepper.com for more information about the new Pepper Perks program.

Dr Pepper graciously sent me two cans prior to their release. The flavor is a good mix of chocolate and Dr Pepper (cherry, almond, and violet). The chocolate flavor tastes very similar to Zuberfizz CocoFizz soda. 

Thank you, Dr Pepper for the soda!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 14, 2021 tagging @hyvee, @hersheycompany, @hersheys, and @reeses. May be an image of food.

node.text: Reese's Bats are here for Halloween! I found them at Hy-Vee.

Aha! Turns out I'm blind, and Mtn Dew Code Red Zero Sugar is very much up on Hy-Vee's website. The soda is not out in stores yet, but I imagine it will be soon. I'm not sure if this is replacing the Diet Code Red. I also don't know if this is regional or a nationwide release.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 13, 2021 tagging @hersheycompany, and @hersheys.

node.text: Vampire Hershey's Kisses are back for Halloween! These are milk chocolate with a strawberry flavored filling. I found them at Woodman's.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 13, 2021 tagging @hyvee, and @jellybellycandyco. May be an image of candy and indoor.

node.text:
New Jelly Belly Apple Cider Mix beans are out now for the fall. These are a mix of red apple and cinnamon flavored jelly beans. I found them at Hy-Vee.

I was so excited when I first spotted these on Jelly Belly's website a few months ago. In the fall of 1997 (I think, give or take a year), Jelly Belly had a seasonal apple cider flavored bean. It was without doubt my favorite Jelly Belly flavor I've ever tried. I even kept the empty bag from the beans in the back of our minivan so I could smell it. I was thinking this mix was the same amazing apple cider flavor... Until I read the description. 😔 I want those apple cider beans back.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by CandyHunting on August 12, 2021 tagging @pepsico, and @mountaindew. May be an image of drink.

node.text:
Mountain Dew Spark is back for a limited time, again as a Speedway exclusive! This Dew is raspberry lemonade flavored.

News and images via PepsiCo.

Some of the Mountain Dew flavors are getting a new look! These new box graphics for Code Red, Live Wire, and Voltage are up on Hy-Vee's website.

Yay or nay on the redesigns?

node.text:
Dunkin's fall menu officially launches on Wednesday, August 18! The menu features the new Pumpkin Cream Cold Brew and Apple Cranberry Refresher. The Pumpkin Spice Signature Latte, pumpkin flavored coffee drinks, apple cider donut, and pumpkin donut, muffin, and donut holes are also returning this season. 

News and image via Dunkin'.
